# Readme

This is lucapost gentoo overlay, for ebuild out of official portage.

## Install

First off all download this repo in your directory (for example ~/repo):
     
     cd ~/repo
     git clone git://github.com/lucapostregna/lucapost-overlay.git

Add path of this overlay to /etc/make.conf (need root):

     PORTDIR_OVERLAY="/home/lucapost/repo/lucapost-overlay"
